hiveArticle.title: FoodPhotography - Healthy Food
hiveArticle.body:
It's always good to have healthy food once in a while, so today morning was that one day. It's called Sprouts Salad which contains Sprouts, Tomato, Cucumber, Curd, Onion and some bhujia just for taste. 

In our busy life it's necessary to keep check on your health, though it cannot be done always but do have health food once in a while.
